{"tid":1687453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"致和理非」 今日準時三點鐘到維園，勿遲到","createTime":"2019-11-02T00:18:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T06:17:55.000Z","uid":8948,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"e017271ba3280fe94ed15e255de9fe7e9a6c6bc7","tid":1687453,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:18:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: small;\"><strong>【突發】11.2愛丁堡、遮打、尖沙咀不反對已批！11.2  100萬級流水式和平集會 真正部署！</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府你以為112打壓維園添馬，香港人就會投降？有無諗過有人晨早為112做好幾手準備？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n無錯，當警察著眼維園、添馬開口牌，香港人喺<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">112愛丁堡、遮打 已經獲得不反對通知書！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n同時間，根據選舉條例第12(5)條，<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">超過100位候選人已決定11.2 下午3點喺維園 舉辦合法選舉聚會</span></span></strong>，各自同全港市民作出區選交流。<br />\n<br />\n維園合法選舉聚會後，大家可<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">以環保方式，大批移動到有 不反對通知書嘅 中環愛丁堡廣場 同 遮打花園</span></span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins><span style=\"font-size: large;\">112 「求援國際 堅守自治」公民活動日真正run down如下：</span></ins></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">- 3pm - 5pm: 到維園支持 逾100位候選人合法選舉聚會<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 環保方式前往 中環<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環愛丁堡廣場一帶 （美國集會已批不反）<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環遮打花園一帶 （紙鶴活動已批不反）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而原訂到維園、添馬嘅嘉賓、器材、物質，將會移到愛丁堡廣場同遮打花園。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府唔好以為到時封鐵，阻止過海會有用。實不相瞞，我地香港人<strong>一早為 尖沙咀柏麗大道112集會拎埋 不反對通知書</strong>。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">假如封過海交通，尖沙咀應變計劃就會啟動。到時，香港人會移師到 尖沙咀柏麗大道 參加流水式和平集會。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n最後，112 「求援國際 堅守自治」集會已經得到<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">全球45個城市，17個國家同步響應，支援香港</span></strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n為自己，為下一代，香港人係時候再次挺身而出，重演百萬人上街畫面，堅守自治，求援國際，光復香港。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人，11.2全球見</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XYGPmRk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXYGPmRk.jpg&h=068a856c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/X2396h2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FX2396h2.gif&h=3a35acf1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n寧化飛灰 不作浮塵</span></span></strong></blockquote>"},{"pid":"1a4fc1e948af625a469061f22e4521722e04e183","tid":1687453,"uid":74155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:19:23.000Z","msg":"無文具嘅就早啲到啦"},{"pid":"30a0c3dd22b40f8304521b2ce05df6b22059a518","tid":1687453,"uid":69916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:19:52.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"01fec9d6b2e31ad5b5e81fc4d164dd836a1c4bdf","tid":1687453,"uid":199471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d6266fbdec62b1e4772a7aa768982c46ce3181","tid":1687453,"uid":89074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:21:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75f57f16a82b3fe53a9d8d13051f7458d0fe07f6","tid":1687453,"uid":204227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T00:21:05.000Z","msg":"點解依加嘅活動愈黎愈晏開始嘅<br />\n運動前期嗰陣嘅活動唔係點半到兩點開始架咩"},{"pid":"10a4f697ab4147d4080efdcd4dba0a14b08a8aa3","tid":1687453,"uid":290176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e017271ba3280fe94ed15e255de9fe7e9a6c6bc7","tid":1687453,"uid":8948,"like":0,"